# Newsletter persistence via JSONBin.io (https://jsonbin.io) — free tier
#
# Steps to enable cloud persistence:
# 1. Sign up at https://jsonbin.io (free)
# 2. Create a new Bin with initial content: {"subscribers": []}
# 3. Copy your Access Key and Bin ID into a .env file (NOT .env.example):

VITE_JSONBIN_ACCESS_KEY=your_access_key_here
VITE_JSONBIN_BIN_ID=your_bin_id_here

# Without these vars, emails are still stored in localStorage
# so the UI works — you just can't retrieve them from a central location.
